snippet.title: Alter Army Trailer
snippet.description:
Alter Army is a fast paced action platformer.
Explore the dying civilization and find out what happened and why you're here.

Alter Army is coming out on 6thh August 2018 so if you like the trailer wishlist the game on steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/602300/Alter_Army/

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/alterarmy/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/alterarmy
Email: vaguepixels@gmail.com / alterarmy@gmail.com
